### Base URL
@baseUrl = https://localhost:8443

### Test server (health check / root)
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

###

### Example GET (adjust endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api
Accept: application/json

###

### Example GET by ID (edit path if needed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Example POST
POST {{baseUrl}}/api
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Name",
  "description": "Sample data"
}

###

### Example PUT
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Name"
}

###

### Example DELETE
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/1